{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 135207, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 因为动摇了执政的合法性", "timestamp": 1594810518, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135228, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 执政的合法性具体是指？", "timestamp": 1594810741, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135250, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 动用军队向平民开枪还不够动摇吗...", "timestamp": 1594810847, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135298, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: ？那美国怎么还存在", "timestamp": 1594811300, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135314, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 美国政府合法性来自人民选举，而且美国这些历史账都已经算过了。", "timestamp": 1594811414, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135351, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: \n暴徒打砸店铺，好！\n军队鸣枪示警，不好！", "timestamp": 1594811784, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135354, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 算过了？什么时候算过的？", "timestamp": 1594811811, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135364, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 为什么民选政府就有动用军队镇压人民的权利？？不应该全都推到民选二字头上吧？", "timestamp": 1594811941, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "政权的合法性是由宪法赋予的，而一部真正的宪法应当是由整体国民共同制定的，即执政党与其他反对党。显然，我们的宪法是缺乏部分合法性的。", "timestamp": 1594813741, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135679, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 政权合法性是民众集体授予的，宪法只是一种形式。一党制下的人民代表同样具有整体国民的代表资格。", "timestamp": 1594815588, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135707, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 理论意义上的确有，实际意义是否有值得商榷。", "timestamp": 1594815857, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135857, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: ....实际上可以代表整体国民吗？还是说不能代表的部分被开除出了“人民”群体并且被专政掉了？", "timestamp": 1594817764, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 136023, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那次事件只有6.4一天吗？", "timestamp": 1594820060, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 136045, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 任何一种代表制度都不可能代表到绝对意义上的100%啊。所以您认为哪部分是被开除并专政掉了呢？", "timestamp": 1594820398, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 136168, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 23254, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 所谓的100%并不是指所有人，而是说每一个阶层的代表都需要参与。建国时除了工人阶级、农民阶级和被团结的部分民族资本家，其他不是都被忽略了吗？当然，其实关于合法性的问题根本不值得讨论，毛主席说了嘛，枪杆子里出政权。", "timestamp": 1594821893, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 23254, "reply": 15, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "#政治相关#\n64为什么会成为敏感点？", "timestamp": 1594810484, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782594, "url": "", "vote": {}}}